</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">IMDagger</dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 06 Oct 2010 23:27:39 +0300</pubDate><guid>tag:,2010-10-06:posts/2010/10/06/pora-lechit/</guid><category>Я</category><category>безумие</category><category>работа</category></item><item><title></title><link>/posts/2010/10/05/urn:ya.ru:post/22199227/1134/</link><description>&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="pgcss-gp"&gt;root@crazyman#&lt;/span&gt; /etc/rc.d/rc.soul restart
